videoData.title: Are you an ideal team player?
videoData.socialTitle: Are you an ideal team player?
videoData.description: It's time to change the way we prepare people for success, says Patrick Lencioni. Drawing from his own observations, he makes a compelling case that, in our increasingly team-oriented world, the key to success is being humble, ambitious and smart.
